{"tid":2426610,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【新鐵路盤巡禮】錦上路站逾2200伙新供應 擬拆兩期數賣","createTime":"2021-02-28T08:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T14:18:03.000Z","uid":166360,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6a8683cc17d8f57830c52bc96c1fd2c48cb7c075","tid":2426610,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:00:00.000Z","msg":"【新鐵路盤巡禮】錦上路站逾2200伙新供應 擬拆兩期數賣<br />\n11:00 2021/02/28<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......信置年報顯示，錦上路站發展項目第1期共約2,200伙單位，將再細分兩個住宅期數推出，第1期涉1,520伙，而第2期約680伙，預計於2022或2023年度取得入伙紙，並預期於2023或2024年度取得轉讓同意書......<br />\n<br />\n......戶型介乎1房至4房單位。錦上路站發展項目第1期不設商場，預計第2期或涉及一個面積43.1萬平方呎的商場......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2888283/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%9B%A4%E5%B7%A1%E7%A6%AE%E3%80%91%E9%8C%A6%E4%B8%8A%E8%B7%AF%E7%AB%99%E9%80%BE2200%E4%BC%99%E6%96%B0%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%20%E6%93%AC%E6%8B%86%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%95%B8%E8%B3%A3%20?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2888283%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%2590%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%25B7%25A1%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%258C%25A6%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25AB%2599%25E9%2580%25BE2200%25E4%25BC%2599%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%2520%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%25B3%25A3%2520%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3vrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=1a6c6a52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2888283/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%9B%A4%E5%B7%A1%E7%A6%AE%E3%80%91%E9%8C%A6%E4%B8%8A%E8%B7%AF%E7%AB%99%E9%80%BE2200%E4%BC%99%E6%96%B0%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%20%E6%93%AC%E6%8B%86%E5%85%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%95%B8%E8%B3%A3%20?mtc=60037</a><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><br />\n大家覺得錦上路站發展潛力如何?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a84314b4615efd9e001462aca563d55d70c46f32","tid":2426610,"uid":128210,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedB