s/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec209cd14f5d1128bff08f45ca96e6e928f54cd","tid":2426610,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd2761350b1d4d6163cf7896d7d1b38a0e264266","tid":2426610,"uid":120499,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:42:06.000Z","msg":"之前成日去嗰度泊車，竟然依家話要起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰度朝早搭西鐵等食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:46:48.000Z","msg":"幾年前香港乜事都無果陣平均真係等兩班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無人落車真係好難逼上車<br />\n有一個人落車通常就逼返四五個人上車<br />\n見過有大肚婆企門邊果個玻璃位啲人係咁衝上車就逼死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfac97f663c659e77c5e798aae2aa00df056b28","tid":2426610,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfe0b6f3e480724cea83f782d52136c2099c470a","tid":2426610,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:33:31.000Z","msg":"大西北仲加人口想點<br />\n遲啲又起屯門南站又起洪水橋站<br />\n錦上路平時繁忙時間已經上唔到車喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:47:07.000Z","msg":"有排加<br />\n仲有 元朗南 洪水橋發展區"}]}